Ttyworker is a PHP framework that allows you to set up modules for existing web sites 
very quickly but it can also be used to create a website or application from beginning to end. 
Ttyworker will be divided into several parts: Tty Blogframe to be primarily for the implementation of blog system. 
tty Cms Ttyworker framework

How to begin

Variable to know

com $ for transmitting data to views
$ this-> right ['name of your method to protect'] is used to temporarily remove the rights to the action performed.
$ editor that enables the textarea
self:: $ com ['model'] for the return of sql query

To create a module there are three branch.
private to the modules that the operation of the application
public for modules that will be directly displayed
Then the core modules that are programmed by the creator

Example of a module called News:
for a minimum must be on file with controller news.php declaration as a class called NewsController with at least one method NewsController Index and then in the Templates folder with a class called NewsModel a method NewsModel.
